headline: What Analyst Projections for Key Metrics Reveal About Equinix (EQIX) Q3 Earnings
summary: Besides Wall Street's top-and-bottom-line estimates for Equinix (EQIX), review projections for some of its key metrics to gain a deeper understanding of how the company might have fared during the quarter ended September 2025.
